"{\"uid\": \"buzzfeednews.com-article-leylamohammed-boxer-imane-khelif-anti-trans-media-frenzy-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Algerian female boxer, who has faced heaps of false, anti-trans speculation around her gender over the past week, was recently misgendered by the president of the International Boxing Association during a press conference.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9751770654307192, \"rank\": 0.023462945879132717, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 167, \"end\": 199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 4.717549363078331e-13, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"BuzzFeed Staff  Many of these people based their claims on the fact that Imane was disqualified from the women's world championship last year after she failed to meet the International Boxing Association's* gender eligibility criteria, per theAssociated Press.Reportsclaimed that this was because Imane had high testosterone levels.\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 4.717549363078331e-13, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, there has never been evidence of this - nor has there been evidence of Imane having XY chromosomes, as theWashington Post noted.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 698, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 654, \"end\": 668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"XY chromosomes\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"*The International Boxing Association wasstripped of its authorityby the International Olympic Committee (IOC) last year due to \\\"its failure to complete reforms on governance, finance and ethical issues.\\\"\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 705, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 4.717549363078331e-13, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 773, \"end\": 810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What's more, Imane has been very vocal about what it was like partaking in boxing as a young girl from a rural village in Tiaret, Algeria.\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1028, \"end\": 1034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiaret\", \"score\": 0.999998971783799, \"rank\": 1.0282172694745524e-06, \"text\": \"Tiaret\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiaret\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiaret\"}, {\"begin\": 1036, \"end\": 1043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.999882998927394, \"rank\": 7.879907093960772e-05, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She toldUNICEFearlier this year, \\\"I particularly want to inspire girls and children who are disadvantaged in Algeria.\\\"\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1154, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.999882998927394, \"rank\": 7.879907093960772e-05, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After winning her match against Anna on Saturday, Imane toldreporters, \\\"I want to tell the entire world that I am a female, and I will remain a female.\\\"\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"score\": 0.9881323208197339, \"rank\": 0.006337624157582949, \"text\": \"Anna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I dedicate this medal to the world, and to all the Arabs, and I tell you, 'Long live Algeria!'\\\"\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1371, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabs\", \"score\": 0.9786286924890023, \"rank\": 0.02064776539156893, \"text\": \"Arabs\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabs\"}, {\"begin\": 1405, \"end\": 1412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.999882998927394, \"rank\": 7.879907093960772e-05, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"she said.\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was something that harms human dignity,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1481, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And this is what affected me at the end of the match.\\\"\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1537, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They took advantage of the media campaign against me to affect me,\\\" she said of Angela's camp.\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BuzzFeed Staff\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1636, \"end\": 1644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BuzzFeed\", \"score\": 0.9995038647099758, \"rank\": 0.0004963815624342742, \"text\": \"BuzzFeed\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BuzzFeed\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BuzzFeed\"}]}]}"